{"tid":2146174,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"經民聯強烈譴責美國制裁行動　指粗暴干涉中國內政","createTime":"2020-08-08T11:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T12:11:43.000Z","uid":221913,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"40b6f4ff67057827d2b3dac323edbaee7473eb29","tid":2146174,"uid":221913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:51:40.000Z","msg":"經民聯發表聲明，強烈譴責美國政府制裁11名中央及香港官員及前官員，稱美國政府嚴重違反國際法和國際關係基本準則，粗暴干涉香港事務和中國內政。經民聯批評，美國的制裁是「赤裸裸的霸權行為」，敦促美國停止「損人不利己」的行為，以免對中美關係及經貿合作，造成更大傷害。經民聯又指，新型肺炎疫情在全球肆虐，美國的政客應該做好國內防疫抗疫，不要到處干涉其他國家事務，成為「麻煩製造者」。<br />\n<br />\n2020-08-08 19:47:43"},{"pid":"bdd87f35de5547dd8fab93317d89b80905a44069","tid":2146174,"uid":274435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:52:32.000Z","msg":"我係支持美國霸權，吹撚漲？"},{"pid":"1e7f78264d28108a73f60144388c4fbc02a7da94","tid":2146174,"uid":221913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LnA339a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLnA339a.gif&h=6bd5e7e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2354212db7eb5c07fc10388e140a2d1bcbe5e26c","tid":2146174,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:54:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1e97a1c1da1e004e4bb2c6fd8431b8c2fb121c9","tid":2146174,"uid":83713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:55:11.000Z","msg":"林健鋒、大口狗同老鼠芬唔係覺得自己走得甩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4cdb1f27c8864aaf4587e8b066047f11bfa2595","tid":2146174,"uid":110579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:56:09.000Z","msg":"同美帝有經貿合作唔算勾結外國勢力咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ad2a207707cd93a22ed510bbedc17f79861ab6","tid":2146174,"uid":221913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T